Name: Average resolution time following 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Median time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Difference in average time between 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time preceding 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total time incidents spend in 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Longest time taken from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E8EF99C100> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest time taken from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to the next 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Comparison of time taken from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Resolved' with 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Elapsed time analysis for cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before reaching 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Time efficiency comparison between 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in leading to case closure
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
